      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and absolutely no scratches, chips, or dings. Inside, the cabin looks and smells brand new, with the leather and trim showing zero signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been garage-kept and maintained to the highest possible standards. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
