      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly starter vehicle? This car is in poor condition and is ready for some serious TLC to get it back to its former glory! It's a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast to roll up their sleeves and bring a classic ride back to life at a great price!",
