    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Get ready to enjoy the road in this well-maintained and reliable vehicle! It's in good condition, showing pride of ownership with a clean interior and a smooth ride that you can count on. It\u2019s a fantastic choice for anyone looking for a quality car that\u2019s ready for many more miles of adventures!",
