      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable choice for someone looking for a functional daily driver. The engine starts reliably and the car drives well, though there is some minor oil weeping and the brakes will likely need servicing within the next few thousand miles. Cosmetically, the exterior has several noticeable door dings and some clear coat peeling on the roof, while the interior shows moderate wear and a small tear on the driver's side upholstery. Overall, it is a solid, honest car that performs its basic duties but lacks the polish of a newer or better-maintained model.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast. Every facet of this automobile\u2014from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior appointments\u2014has been maintained to exacting standards. This is an investment-grade example that offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery, catering to those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute gem. This car is in incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it strictly in the garage, and never missed a service. It\u2019s spotless inside and out, runs like a total dream, and is ready for its next adventure. You won't find another one this clean! Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43250.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a definitive example of the S54-powered masterpiece. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been fully overhauled to ensure optimal cam timing and volumetric efficiency. Power is routed through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via an M Variable Differential Lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to maintain structural rigidity under high lateral G-loads. The suspension retains its factory-correct geometry, providing the telepathic steering feedback these chassis are known for. With no rod bearing concerns and a pristine undercarriage, this vehicle is mechanically synchronized and ready for the most demanding collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    }
